    "contentType": "text",
    "content": "<h3>Integration Launch Room is live</h3><p>Purpose: This private space is for tracking progress, managing beta insights, and coordinating our go-live.</p><ul><li><b>Integration Planning Board</b> (Planner): Track milestones, owners, and due dates.</li><li><b>Feedback &amp; QA Center</b> (SharePoint): Collect QA findings, triage issues, and store artifacts.</li><li><b>Integration Runbook</b> (OneNote): Document procedures, checklists, and rollback steps.</li></ul><p>Members: <at id=\"0\">Alice Johnson</at>, <at id=\"1\">Bob Smith</at>, <at id=\"2\">Sophia Bennett</at></p><p>Let\u2019s keep all coordination here to reduce noise and accelerate the rollout.</p>"
